---
import '../styles/global.css';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
const { title = SITE_TITLE, description = SITE_DESCRIPTION } = Astro.props;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="description" content={description} />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-background text-foreground antialiased font-mono">
        <!-- AI Disclaimer Banner -->
        <div class="bg-accent text-background px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <span>⚠️ 주의: 이 사이트의 모든 콘텐츠와 코드는 AI 에이전트 '오딩'에 의해 100% 자동 생성되었습니다.</span>
        </div>
		<slot />
	</body>
</html>
